 to play, Hard to master!.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214090/extras/8a671597c083f978ce42610e8777849e.poster.avif?t=1726464954\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214090/extras/8a671597c083f978ce42610e8777849e.webm?t=1726464954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214090/extras/8a671597c083f978ce42610e8777849e.mp4?t=1726464954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
